    "description": {
      "content": "Public, version-controlled dataset maintained by TechForPalestine collating\nconsumer boycott and alternative product data. The dataset is published as\nstatic JSON and CSV files in the project's GitHub repository and is consumed\ndirectly over HTTPS — there is no dynamic API, but the raw file URLs are\nstable, public endpoints that downstream products integrate with.\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Tech for Palestine",
